    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Race Mode is here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's time to settle the score in a 1v1 race to the top. Enter the race-exclusive stage with your friend!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you take the turtle path, steady and reliable, or the rabbit path, risky but fast? The moment you choose, the race has already begun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s Finally Here! Multiplayer Mode Unlocked! Grab a friend by the Crowbar and Climb to the Top – Together!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/df3440dd1cf8f2aafd84a611163e4ba5.poster.avif?t=1770953749\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/df3440dd1cf8f2aafd84a611163e4ba5.webm?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/df3440dd1cf8f2aafd84a611163e4ba5.mp4?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This game is a challenge for all VR gamers who love physics and brain teasers.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For VR gamers who are strong in both mind and arm... see you at the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💪Your hands are crowbars—ready to start climbing💪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Crowbar Climber</i>, use your crowbars to make your way up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face hooks, planks, and gears using only your arms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you beat the game before you run out of energy?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/feecb70e59eaa45724d412abac16d1f9.poster.avif?t=1770953749\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/feecb70e59eaa45724d412abac16d1f9.webm?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/feecb70e59eaa45724d412abac16d1f9.mp4?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧗‍♂️Master the art of climbing through physics!🧗‍♀️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control your environment and body using a crowbar that reacts to every move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab hooks at the last second, launch yourself with powerful swings, and cling to ledges in creative ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff4582466d14d300cfa77414bd0af19d.poster.avif?t=1770953749\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff4582466d14d300cfa77414bd0af19d.webm?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff4582466d14d300cfa77414bd0af19d.mp4?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📷Share your gameplay videos with friends!🎥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Record both first-person and third-person perspectives, just like in the promo video.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your crowbar-climbing skills to friends or share on social media.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff43d56aa9c0b4921c64bfaf5af365bb.poster.avif?t=1770953749\" width=674 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff43d56aa9c0b4921c64bfaf5af365bb.webm?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285300/extras/ff43d56aa9c0b4921c64bfaf5af365bb.mp4?t=1770953749\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
